  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@value" : "CQ: Crushing and Milling\nWhat is the particle size and size distribution of the mining waste?"
  }, {
    "@value" : "MINNERSA, SGS\nIn this case, it is the classification of a mineral's size. A particle size analysis determines the proportion of minerals in different fractions. This is an important characteristic when processing minerals."
  } ]
}, {
